<plot>Hosted by 'Eva Marie Saint' (qv), the film's leading lady, this 40-minute documentary of 'Alfred Hitchcock (I)' (qv)'s only M-G-M film combines interviews ('Martin Landau' (qv), 'Patricia Hitchcock' (qv), production designer 'Robert F. Boyle' (qv) and screenwriter 'Ernest Lehman' (qv)), movie clips and behind the scenes photos to make for a fascinating look at one of the silver screen's glowing gems. For fans of _North by Northwest (1959)_ (qv) and Hitchcock aficionados, this is a must see treat.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?142398</url></doc>
